entries.s_35: I have a list of ship parts that I need to fix a YT-1300.
entries.s_36: I should be able to sell them to you. It's a YT-1300, you say? You wouldn't happen to be talking about the Millennium Falcon, would you?
entries.s_38: How am I ever going to get this into the inventory?
entries.s_39: Then your money isn't any good here. I won't supply you with anything.
entries.s_40: Then how am I supposed to get off this station?
entries.s_41: That's not my problem. Go bother someone in the Cantina or something.
